    {
      "role": "user",
      "content": "it doesn't feel freeing though. it just feels hollow. like there's nothing left to actually \"embrace.\" if the person who had the dreams and the spark is gone, then what am i even doing here? it feels like i'm just taking up space that doesn't belong to me anymore.",
