      "content": "\"burn the old one down\"... that sounds so final. it's just that everything feels so heavy and pointless. sometimes i look at the empty space in my life and i think, if the spark is really gone for good, then why keep dragging this shell around? what's the point of maintaining a life that's already empty?",
